snippet.title: Fowl Damage - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Fowl Damage is an atmospheric puzzle platformer developed by May Gardens and Red Nexus Games Inc. Players will manage jumps and falls through the expansive world filled with challenging puzzles and intense boss fights. Fowl Damage is launching on September 13 for PC (Steam).

#Gaming #GameTrailers #Games
